1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:01:34,879 --> 00:01:36,040
I want to see my master!

3
00:01:36,239 --> 00:01:37,560
Let me see him!

4
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:40,079
Do you hear me?

5
00:01:40,079 --> 00:01:41,400
Let me see my master!

6
00:01:42,079 --> 00:01:43,000
Guards!

7
00:01:43,879 --> 00:01:45,680
Stop shouting. You're a dead woman.

8
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:46,439
No need to yell.

9
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:47,760
Yes, I'm dying.

10
00:01:48,239 --> 00:01:49,120
But I don't want to take

11
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:50,519
Lady Cheng'en's secret to my grave.

12
00:01:51,239 --> 00:01:52,719
I won't tell that secret

13
00:01:52,719 --> 00:01:53,640
without seeing Master Wu.

14
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:55,680
Take me to him now!

15
00:02:06,260 --> 00:02:10,140
=Episode 19=

16
00:02:23,479 --> 00:02:25,479
Master Wu is truly devoted

17
00:02:25,759 --> 00:02:27,719
to you, Your Highness.

18
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,680
Why stop me?

19
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:34,159
Your Highness,

20
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:36,479
I fear

21
00:02:36,919 --> 00:02:38,759
that if you praise him again,

22
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:40,439
he will clash
with Lady Cheng'en once more.

23
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,719
Those who deserved punishment got it.

24
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:44,319
Those who needed comfort received it.

25
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:47,759
If they're sensible, they won't
cause more trouble.

26
00:03:03,599 --> 00:03:04,240
Your Highness,

27
00:03:04,599 --> 00:03:05,400
Wu Lian.

28
00:03:05,919 --> 00:03:08,400
Your people made a mistake,

29
00:03:08,599 --> 00:03:09,879
so you should be punished too.

30
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:13,479
But your embroidery is exquisite.

31
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,960
So I'll punish you...

32
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,639
How should I punish you?

33
00:03:20,919 --> 00:03:22,039
I accept any punishment.

34
00:03:22,319 --> 00:03:24,199
Now, I can't think of anything.

35
00:03:25,039 --> 00:03:25,840
No hurry.

36
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:28,439
You can punish me whenever
you remember.

37
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,000
Right now,

38
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:33,000
I'm at a critical point in
embroidering "National Beauty."

39
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:35,240
I dare not be careless.

40
00:03:36,199 --> 00:03:37,000
All right.

41
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:46,800
(With the Princess Consort
as my shield,)

42
00:03:47,719 --> 00:03:50,199
(no matter what Lin Rulan does,)

43
00:03:50,479 --> 00:03:52,039
(she can't touch me.)

44
00:03:58,080 --> 00:03:59,439
Careless fool.

45
00:03:59,759 --> 00:04:00,800
What's the matter?

46
00:04:00,919 --> 00:04:02,599
Ms. Meng has gone crazy.

47
00:04:02,719 --> 00:04:03,840
She wants to see Master Wu.

48
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:05,240
She has a secret to tell.

49
00:04:05,919 --> 00:04:07,000
What secret?

50
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:12,879
Your Highness, do you want to go
to the prison and see?

51
00:04:14,719 --> 00:04:15,759
No need.

52
00:04:16,879 --> 00:04:19,160
I have no interest in secrets.

53
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:22,600
I only know that
before the Prince returns,

54
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:25,480
nothing can go wrong in this manor.

55
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:28,199
Will you let Master Wu go?

56
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,120
That's up to him.

57
00:04:30,319 --> 00:04:33,839
He can handle his own people.

58
00:04:34,199 --> 00:04:36,439
As long as he doesn't cause
trouble for the manor.

59
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:37,839
Yes.

60
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,240
My Lady.

61
00:04:48,079 --> 00:04:48,920
What's wrong?

62
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,600
Wu Lian went to the manor prison.

63
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,839
Why?

64
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:54,160
I heard Meng Wan wants to
tell him a secret.

65
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:55,279
To see him,

66
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,360
she's gone crazy.

67
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:58,600
Oh no.

68
00:04:58,680 --> 00:04:59,439
My Lady.

69
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:00,920
Don't follow me.

70
00:05:01,199 --> 00:05:02,680
If I'm not back in half an hour,

71
00:05:02,839 --> 00:05:03,720
go find Mr. Liu.

72
00:05:09,879 --> 00:05:11,879
Her Highness is resting.

73
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:13,560
Please come back tomorrow.

74
00:05:13,639 --> 00:05:14,639
If it were my personal matter,

75
00:05:14,639 --> 00:05:15,439
I could come back tomorrow.

76
00:05:15,439 --> 00:05:16,480
But if it's about the manor,

77
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:17,720
aren't you afraid the sky will fall?

78
00:05:22,959 --> 00:05:23,759
Wenyue.

79
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:25,160
Ruoheng.

80
00:05:25,519 --> 00:05:26,879
What's the matter now?

81
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:28,079
She said

82
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:31,480
the sky over the manor will
fall tomorrow.

83
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:33,480
Leave us.

84
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:35,240
I want to hear

85
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:37,560
how the sky will fall.

86
00:05:45,439 --> 00:05:46,079
Wenyue,

87
00:05:46,879 --> 00:05:48,199
I have a request.

88
00:05:49,199 --> 00:05:50,000
Speak.

89
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:52,040
I've thought it over.

90
00:05:52,399 --> 00:05:54,879
Our deal wasn't fair to me.

91
00:05:56,319 --> 00:05:57,560
You want to back out?

92
00:05:58,040 --> 00:05:58,959
Don't be angry.

93
00:05:59,519 --> 00:06:00,839
To keep me from backing out,

94
00:06:01,519 --> 00:06:04,160
you just need to grant me
one act of merit.

95
00:06:06,279 --> 00:06:07,079
I'm listening.

96
00:06:08,079 --> 00:06:09,639
Since childhood, I've done
good deeds.

97
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:11,920
I never wanted to stain my
hands with killing.

98
00:06:12,439 --> 00:06:15,680
But for you, I took that
sterilization medicine

99
00:06:15,839 --> 00:06:16,959
to put your mind at ease.

100
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:19,040
And yet, I feel uneasy.

101
00:06:19,439 --> 00:06:21,399
I think of all the children

102
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,000
who never got to be born.

103
00:06:24,279 --> 00:06:25,480
Is that all?

104
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:28,360
There's a Buddhist hall in the manor.

105
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,879
Once you're settled in,

106
00:06:30,199 --> 00:06:32,600
I'll have the monks chant
for their souls.

107
00:06:32,839 --> 00:06:34,639
Chanting is good,

108
00:06:34,879 --> 00:06:36,160
but not as good as real action.

109
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:39,000
Today, I came to tell you

110
00:06:39,399 --> 00:06:40,279
that saving one life

111
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:42,120
is what matters the most.

112
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:43,600
Save whom?

113
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,959
Those people you mentioned,

114
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:48,399
I already had Magistrate Yu
release them.

115
00:06:48,439 --> 00:06:51,680
I want you to save Meng Wan.

116
00:06:52,439 --> 00:06:54,240
Someone from Yanyu Embroidery House?

117
00:06:54,879 --> 00:06:56,279
Why would you want to save her?

118
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:58,279
Yes, she's from that house.

119
00:06:58,319 --> 00:06:59,720
But you have keen eyes.

120
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:01,120
You must see

121
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:04,680
that Ms. Meng is just
Wu Lian's mouth

122
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:06,079
and hands.

123
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:08,199
We are both women.

124
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,439
Think carefully.

125
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:12,680
When has Ms. Meng ever
done wrong?

126
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:15,079
Every time she speaks, it's for Wu Lian.

127
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:16,920
True.

128
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:20,120
The pheasant's severed head,
I was the one who found it.

129
00:07:20,879 --> 00:07:23,439
You were angry, so you
ordered her killed.

130
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:25,560
But

131
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:28,959
I don't want more killing between us.

132
00:07:30,519 --> 00:07:31,319
Wenyue,

133
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:33,079
just having me here

134
00:07:33,279 --> 00:07:34,879
is already a blessing.

135
00:07:35,319 --> 00:07:37,839
But I'm afraid.

136
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:41,160
I'm afraid Ms. Meng will haunt me
in my dreams.

137
00:07:43,199 --> 00:07:44,399
Is that all?

138
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:06,439
Be good. After the Flower Festival,

139
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:07,879
I'll release her.

140
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:10,959
Thank you, Wenyue.

141
00:08:11,519 --> 00:08:13,040
Since you've agreed,

142
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:15,879
your word is as good as gold.

143
00:08:16,439 --> 00:08:17,759
Now, I can rest easy.

144
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:39,960
Asking you to come to a place like this.

145
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:43,320
You must resent me.

146
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:45,039
You've already confessed.

147
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:48,840
Why lure me here with a secret?

148
00:08:48,879 --> 00:08:51,039
I've been by your side for years.

149
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:53,600
Taking this secret to my grave

150
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:55,600
doesn't sit right with me.

151
00:08:57,519 --> 00:08:59,279
For the sake of our years together,

152
00:09:00,279 --> 00:09:01,080
speak.

153
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:06,360
I don't know Lady Cheng'en's secret.

154
00:09:07,799 --> 00:09:09,080
But I know

155
00:09:11,519 --> 00:09:14,799
I destroyed the Princess Consort's gown.

156
00:09:15,519 --> 00:09:17,240
I lured Jia Yi over

157
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:18,600
and sent him to Rulan.

158
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:22,879
Even Xiaoyi's death... I set that trap.

159
00:09:23,399 --> 00:09:25,679
You didn't know any of that, did you?

160
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:29,840
I don't know what you're saying.

161
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:32,360
Are you pretending not to understand?

162
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:34,279
Let me tell you.

163
00:09:34,399 --> 00:09:36,559
The secrets of your embroidery house
won't stay hidden much longer.

164
00:09:37,279 --> 00:09:39,120
Even if you follow the Princess Consort

165
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:39,960
like a loyal dog,

166
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:41,240
she won't be able to save you.

167
00:09:43,519 --> 00:09:45,600
I've treated you well, haven't I?

168
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:48,159
Well?

169
00:09:48,679 --> 00:09:50,080
You defiled me first.

170
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:51,879
Then you killed my sworn sister.

171
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:53,279
You treated us like gifts

172
00:09:53,279 --> 00:09:55,240
between you and your rich friends.

173
00:09:55,919 --> 00:09:56,840
You blackmailed them

174
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:58,600
to keep them silent.

175
00:09:58,679 --> 00:09:59,879
Is that being good to me?

176
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:02,720
You fed your filthy soul with our blood.

177
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:03,679
Is that being good to me?

178
00:10:03,679 --> 00:10:04,399
Wretch!

179
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:12,080
Wu Lian,

180
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:15,039
I'm not the same Meng Wan I used to be.

181
00:10:15,919 --> 00:10:18,559
But you are still the same Wu Lian.

182
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:22,600
Does it matter who you are?

183
00:10:22,919 --> 00:10:24,480
A dead woman.

184
00:10:25,039 --> 00:10:27,440
From the day the pheasant's
head was severed,

185
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:30,000
I never planned to live.

186
00:11:03,620 --> 00:11:06,580
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

187
00:11:06,820 --> 00:11:09,820
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

188
00:11:11,020 --> 00:11:13,780
♪The past no longer binds♪

189
00:11:14,260 --> 00:11:17,980
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

190
00:11:18,420 --> 00:11:22,540
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

191
00:11:23,380 --> 00:11:26,260
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

192
00:11:26,620 --> 00:11:28,620
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

193
00:11:28,620 --> 00:11:32,700
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

194
00:11:33,100 --> 00:11:35,300
♪For your faith that never broke♪

195
00:11:35,500 --> 00:11:39,620
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

196
00:11:40,500 --> 00:11:42,420
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

197
00:11:42,420 --> 00:11:46,660
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

198
00:11:47,860 --> 00:11:50,340
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

199
00:11:50,460 --> 00:11:53,100
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

200
00:11:53,100 --> 00:11:55,700
♪One thought turns into ash♪

201
00:11:56,660 --> 00:12:02,020
♪No future left to write♪

202
00:12:03,100 --> 00:12:04,900
♪If I never fall♪

203
00:12:04,940 --> 00:12:07,300
♪How could this waiting end♪

204
00:12:07,300 --> 00:12:08,660
♪If I bear no scars♪

205
00:12:08,660 --> 00:12:10,980
♪How could I challenge fate♪

206
00:12:10,980 --> 00:12:13,340
♪I knew there was no way back♪

207
00:12:13,340 --> 00:12:17,340
♪Yet I left this hope behind♪

208
00:12:17,460 --> 00:12:19,580
♪For your faith that never broke♪

209
00:12:19,780 --> 00:12:23,740
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

210
00:12:24,700 --> 00:12:26,620
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

211
00:12:26,620 --> 00:12:31,020
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

212
00:12:32,100 --> 00:12:34,700
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

213
00:12:34,740 --> 00:12:37,300
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

214
00:12:37,300 --> 00:12:39,660
♪One thought turns into ash♪

215
00:12:40,780 --> 00:12:46,020
♪No future left to write♪

216
00:12:46,900 --> 00:12:49,300
♪The lamp is out, you're gone♪

217
00:12:50,580 --> 00:12:52,700
♪Heaven and earth fall silent♪

218
00:12:54,380 --> 00:12:56,580
♪If we meet again someday♪

219
00:12:57,020 --> 00:13:02,820
♪This longing sleeps beneath the snow♪

